-T 4 ---> 4 threads per CPU (default)
-T 2C --> 2 threads per CPU

-DskipTests=true - compiles the test and skip running them
-Dmaven.test.skip - skip compile and skip run tests

-pl - makes maven build only specified module and not the whole project
-rf - resume build from the specified project
-U - forces a check for updated dependency on remote repository